    <reapack name="Stemperator_AI_Separate.lua" type="script" desc="Stemperator - AI Stem Separation">
      <version name="1.1.1" author="flarkAUDIO">
        <changelog><![CDATA[v1.1.1: Cross-platform support
- Full Windows, Linux, and macOS compatibility
- Auto-detect Python and ffmpeg paths per platform
- Use correct temp directories and shell commands

v1.1.0: Major update
- Persist settings between sessions (REAPER ExtState)
- Keyboard shortcuts: 1-4 toggle stems, K=Karaoke, I=Instrumental, D=Drums
- 6-stem model support (htdemucs_6s for guitar/piano)
- Quick preset buttons: All, Karaoke, Vocals, Drums]]></changelog>
        <source main="main">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/flarkflarkflark/Stemperator/main/scripts/reaper/Stemperator_AI_Separate.lua</source>
        <source>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/flarkflarkflark/Stemperator/main/scripts/reaper/audio_separator_process.py</source>
      </version>
    </reapack>
